@node Introduction "DarkGlow: Introduction"

                                  Introduction
                                 --------------

   DarkGlow is a plugin for the famous image-manipulation-program
   ArtEffect2/3+. As a normal PlugIn it integrates seamlessly in ArtEffect's
   menu and waits happily for your attention.

   DarkGlow generates darkglowing effects.
   Many options, so make sure to read @{"usage" link Usage}.

   DarkGlow has a close relative where it stems from: Glow.

@endnode

